---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="行動與普適智慧 | NTU CSIE 5411">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-slate-900">
    
    <section class="py-24 flex flex-col items-center text-center px-4 relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-[-10%] left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[600px] h-[400px] bg-cyan-900/30 blur-[120px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>

      <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 text-cyan-400 text-sm font-semibold mb-6 tracking-wider">
        NTU CSIE 5411 • 114-1
      </div>
      
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">
        行動與<span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-500">普適智慧</span>
      </h1>
      
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-300 font-medium mb-4">
        Mobile and Pervasive Intelligence
      </p>

      <p class="text-md md:text-lg text-slate-400 max-w-3xl mb-10 leading-relaxed">
        探索行動平台與普適運算的理論基礎與實務應用。從無所不在的感測器提取未知資訊，並結合邊緣運算與自主系統，打造智慧化的物聯網與機器人應用。
      </p>

      <div class="flex gap-4 z-10">
        <a href="#scca-core" class="px-6 py-3 bg-cyan-600 hover:bg-cyan-500 text-white rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-cyan-500/30">
          探索課程核心
        </a>
        <a href="/labs" class="px-6 py-3 bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-white border border-slate-700 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors">
          進入實驗教材
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="scca-core" class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 pb-24 relative z-10">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">SCCA 課程架構</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400">本課程以四個核心維度 (SCCA) 建構智慧系統的設計原則</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        
        <div class="p-8 bg-slate-800/80 backdrop-blur-sm border border-cyan-500/30 rounded-2xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300 group">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-cyan-900/50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-cyan-400 text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            📡
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Sensation</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
            行動平台的感測與感知能力。探討無線訊號 (Wireless)、視覺 (Visual) 與聲學 (Acoustic) 等先進感測技術。
          </p>
          <div class="text-xs font-mono text-cyan-500/80 bg-cyan-950/50 inline-block px-2 py-1 rounded">Module A1</div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-slate-800/80 backdrop-blur-sm border border-blue-500/30 rounded-2xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300 group">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-900/50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-blue-400 text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            📶
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Communication</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
            先進通訊與網路技術。學習如何將硬體與軟體元件連結，構建穩定且高效的普適系統網路。
          </p>
          <div class="text-xs font-mono text-blue-500/80 bg-blue-950/50 inline-block px-2 py-1 rounded">Module A2</div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-slate-800/80 backdrop-blur-sm border border-indigo-500/30 rounded-2xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300 group">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-indigo-900/50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-400 text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            🧠
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Computing</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
            智慧運算架構。涵蓋情境感知運算 (Context-aware computing)、無伺服器架構與分散式邊緣智慧。
          </p>
          <div class="text-xs font-mono text-indigo-500/80 bg-indigo-950/50 inline-block px-2 py-1 rounded">Module B1</div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-slate-800/80 backdrop-blur-sm border border-purple-500/30 rounded-2xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300 group">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-purple-900/50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-purple-400 text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            🤖
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Autonomy</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
            自主系統與協作。設計無人機、移動機器人等平台之間的自主協調與合作演算法。
          </p>
          <div class="text-xs font-mono text-purple-500/80 bg-purple-950/50 inline-block px-2 py-1 rounded">Module B2</div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="border-t border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/50 py-20">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Hands-on Tutorials & Projects</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
          本課程高度強調實作能力。我們將帶領學生從微控制器到單板電腦，親手打造結合感測、運算與通訊的智慧系統原型。
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-slate-800 px-6 py-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-700">
            <span class="text-2xl">♾️</span>
            <div class="text-left">
              <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">Microcontroller</div>
              <div class="font-bold text-white">Arduino Uno</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-slate-800 px-6 py-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-700">
            <span class="text-2xl">🍓</span>
            <div class="text-left">
              <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">Edge Computing</div>
              <div class="font-bold text-white">Raspberry Pi 4</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>